statements: SELECT * FROM historical_algorithm_data WHERE execution_status = 'SUCCESS';
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time FROM historical_algorithm_data WHERE execution_result = 'Completed';
SELECT execution_id, execution_result FROM historical_algorithm_data WHERE algorithm_name = 'Example Algorithm';
SELECT * FROM historical_algorithm_data ORDER BY execution_time DESC;
SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name, execution_time FROM historical_algorithm_data WHERE execution_result = 'Failed';
SELECT * FROM historical_algorithm_data ORDER BY execution_time DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name FROM historical_algorithm_data WHERE execution_status = 'SUCCESS'
SELECT * FROM historical_algorithm_data WHERE algorithm_name LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY execution_time ASC
SELECT DISTINCT algorithm_name FROM historical_algorithm_data WHERE execution_status = 'FAILURE'
SELECT AVG(execution_time) AS avg_execution_time FROM historical_algorithm_data
SELECT * FROM algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_date FROM algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name, execution_status FROM algorithms WHERE execution_status = 'success';
SELECT * FROM execution_logs ORDER BY log_date_time DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, log_date_time FROM algorithms INNER JOIN execution_logs ON algorithms.algorithm_id = execution_logs.algorithm_id;
SELECT * FROM algorithms WHERE execution_status = 'success';
SELECT algorithm_id, execution_date, execution_time, execution_status FROM algorithms WHERE algorithm_name = 'Algorithm1';

SELECT execution_logs.log_id, execution_logs.log_message, execution_logs.log_date_time, algorithms.algorithm_name FROM execution_logs JOIN algorithms ON execution_logs.algorithm_id = algorithms.algorithm_id;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_date FROM algorithms WHERE algorithm_id IN (1, 2, 3) ORDER BY execution_date DESC;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name, execution_date, execution_time, execution_status FROM algorithms WHERE execution_date >= '2022-01-01' AND execution_status = 'failure';
SELECT * FROM algorithm_execution_data ORDER BY execution_date DESC;
SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name, execution_duration FROM algorithm_execution_data WHERE algorithm_name = 'Algorithm1';
SELECT execution_id, result_code FROM algorithm_execution_data WHERE execution_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT pattern_id, pattern_description FROM execution_patterns ORDER BY pattern_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM execution_trends WHERE trend_value > 100 ORDER BY trend_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM algorithm_execution_data ORDER BY execution_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name, result_code FROM algorithm_execution_data WHERE execution_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY execution_date LIMIT 10;

SELECT execution_id, pattern_description FROM execution_patterns JOIN algorithm_execution_data ON execution_patterns.execution_id = algorithm_execution_data.execution_id WHERE algorithm_name = 'Sorting Algorithm' ORDER BY pattern_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT algorithm_name, COUNT(*) AS num_executions FROM algorithm_execution_data GROUP BY algorithm_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY num_executions DESC;

SELECT a.exectuion_date, b.pattern_description, c.trend_value FROM algorithm_execution_data a JOIN execution_patterns b ON a.execution_id = b.execution_id JOIN execution_trends c ON a.execution_id = c.execution_id WHERE c.trend_type = 'Performance' ORDER BY a.execution_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name, execution_date FROM AlgorithmExecutions WHERE execution_status = 'SUCCESS';
SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name FROM AlgorithmExecutions ORDER BY execution_date DESC;

SELECT * FROM AlgoExecutionData WHERE execution_time_ms > 5000 ORDER BY execution_time_ms DESC;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmExecutions;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_date, execution_time FROM AlgorithmExecutions ORDER BY execution_date DESC;
SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name, execution_date FROM AlgorithmExecutions WHERE execution_status = 'SUCCESS';
SELECT * FROM ExecutionLogs INNER JOIN AlgorithmExecutions ON ExecutionLogs.execution_id = AlgorithmExecutions.execution_id WHERE AlgorithmExecutions.algorithm_name = 'Regression';
SELECT * FROM AlgoExecutionData WHERE execution_time_ms > 1000 ORDER BY execution_time_ms DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT execution_id, algorithm_name, execution_duration FROM algorithm_execution_data WHERE execution_status = 'SUCCESS';
